author: Rhys Falby
title: Understanding Autograde report
question:
Wondering what this report means and how I can fix the issue
 2.1%  of   3.6%  x      Additional tests: incorrect - 2 autograder internal additional tests failed.
student_answer: The autograder ran tests on your code and your code did not produce the correct results
instructor_answer: The report means that your function is not doing what we want it to do.
